# Server Configuration
PORT=5000
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:3000

# Database Configuration (for DBTune itself)
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_USER=dbtune_user
DB_PASSWORD=password
DB_NAME=dbtune_dev

# Test Database Configuration (for Jest tests)
TEST_DB_HOST=localhost
TEST_DB_PORT=5433
TEST_DB_USER=dbtune_test_user
TEST_DB_PASSWORD=test_password
TEST_DB_NAME=dbtune_test

# JWT Secret for authentication
JWT_SECRET=supersecretjwtkeythatshouldbeverylongandrandominproduction

# Encryption Key for sensitive connection data (MUST be 32 characters for AES-256)
ENCRYPTION_KEY=ThisIsA32CharSecretForEncryption

# Other configurations
# LOG_LEVEL=info (default: debug in dev, info in prod)
```

**`Dockerfile` (Multi-stage build for client and server)**
```dockerfile